# 🔍 VulnTracker — CVE Vulnerability Scanner

Real-time CVE vulnerability tracker that fetches latest 
Critical vulnerabilities from NVD database, classifies 
by CVSS score, and integrates with Splunk SIEM.

## Features
- ✅ Fetches live CVE data from NVD API
- ✅ CVSS severity classification
- ✅ Auto-generates JSON incident reports
- ✅ Splunk SIEM integration
- ✅ Prioritized remediation actions

## Tech Stack
Python, NVD API, Splunk, REST API

## How to Run
pip install requests
python src/vulntracker.py

